::xowiki::Page new \
	-set name en:reference_kv_textpage.page \
	-title "Textpage Command Reference" \
	-text {
<p><u>Name:</u></p>
<p>textpage - Create a paragraph of text with a title</p>

<p><u>Synopsis:</u></p>
<p><b>textpage</b> <i>identifier</i> key <i>value</i></p>

<p><u>Description:</u></p>
<p>Creates a textpage based on key-value pairs. The provided <i>identifier</i> is used as an id for the element in order to reference it (e.g.: p1, myContent).</p>

<p>Valid keys are:</p>

<p><b>textpage</b> <i>identifier</i> <b>title</b> title_of_paragraph<br>
<b>textpage</b> <i>identifier</i> <b>body</b> paragraph_text</p>

<p><u>Textpage Example:</u></p>
<code class="example">textpage p1 title "Example Page Title" <br>textpage p1 body "This is some example text for a paragraph"</code>
} \
	-description {Textpage}
